General.Name: Worthington Steel Inc
General.Description: Worthington Steel, Inc. operates as a steel processor in North America. The company offers carbon flat-rolled steel and tailor welded blanks, as well as automotive and electrical steel lamination stampings; and aluminum tailor welded blanks. It serves various end-markets, including automotive, construction, machinery and equipment, heavy truck, agriculture, and energy. The company was incorporated in 2023 and is headquartered in Columbus, Ohio.
